2
00:00:07,592 --> 00:00:08,892
你是我最好的朋友 Barney

3
00:00:08,912 --> 00:00:10,012
很好 那作为你最好的朋友

4
00:00:10,022 --> 00:00:13,382
我提议我们玩个游戏 
我把它叫做"你见过Ted了吗?"

5
00:00:13,402 --> 00:00:15,662
什么? 天啊 我太傻了

6
00:00:15,672 --> 00:00:17,212
呆那儿别动 我这就来了

7
00:00:17,232 --> 00:00:18,522
{\a7}*Say,man*

8
00:00:19,152 --> 00:00:20,552
{\a7}*Don't walk ahead of that woman*

9
00:00:20,562 --> 00:00:22,132
{\a7}*Like she don't belong to you*

10
00:00:23,272 --> 00:00:25,572
{\a7}*Just 'cause her got
them little skinny legs*

11
00:00:25,592 --> 00:00:27,192
{\a7}*You know that ain't no way to do*

12
00:00:29,672 --> 00:00:31,322
{\a7}*You didn't act like
that when you had it home*

13
00:00:31,362 --> 00:00:32,962
{\a7}*Behind closed doors*

14
00:00:33,292 --> 00:00:34,512
{\a7}*All right*

15
00:00:35,632 --> 00:00:38,162
{\a7}*Now you act like you're
ashamed at a woman*

16
00:00:38,872 --> 00:00:41,012
{\a7}*Don't even want nobody
to know she's yours*

17
00:00:41,922 --> 00:00:43,132
{\a7}*But that's all right*

18
00:00:43,392 --> 00:00:45,552
{\a7}*You just walk on,baby *

19
00:00:45,832 --> 00:00:50,422
{\a7}*And don't you worry about 
a doggone thing at all*

20
00:00:47,422 --> 00:00:49,762
{\a10}麦克拉伦酒吧

21
00:00:51,392 --> 00:00:54,652
{\a7}*Because there's some man
somewhere who'll take you*

22
00:00:54,682 --> 00:00:56,322
{\a7}*Baby,skinny legs and all*

23
00:00:56,342 --> 00:00:58,662
非常对不起

24
